---
title: "{{ title }}"
slug: "{{ slug }}"
date: {{ date }}
series: "{{ series }}"
chapter: "{{ chapter }}"
article_variant: "spoiler"
{% if tags %}
tags:
{% for tag in tags %}
  - "{{ tag }}"
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
tags: []
{% endif %}
draft: {{ draft | lower }}
description: "{{ description }}"
affiliate_ids:
  amazon: "{{ affiliate_ids.amazon }}"
  rakuten: "{{ affiliate_ids.rakuten }}"
{% if affiliate_ids.others %}
  others:
{% for other in affiliate_ids.others %}
    - name: "{{ other.name }}"
      url: "{{ other.url }}"
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
  others: []
{% endif %}
disclaimer: "{{ disclaimer }}"
{% if images %}
images:
{% for image in images %}
  - "{{ image }}"
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
images: []
{% endif %}
---
{{ intro }}

> **{{ spoiler_notice | default("本記事は最新話までのネタバレを含みます。") }}**

{% if hero_image %}
![{{ hero_image.alt }}]({{ hero_image.url }})
<small>Photo by <a href="{{ hero_image.photographer_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ hero_image.photographer }}</a> on <a href="{{ hero_image.pexels_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pexels</a></small>
{% endif %}

## 第{{ chapter_label }}のあらすじ（ざっくり概要）
{% for point in summary_points %}
- {{ point }}
{% endfor %}

{{ "{{< spoiler >}}" }}
## 第{{ chapter_label }} 詳細ネタバレ（時系列で詳しく）
{{ spoiler.synopsis }}

## 考察・伏線・キャラの心情分析
{% for item in spoiler.foreshadowings %}
- {{ item }}
{% endfor %}

## 今後の展開予想（あくまで予想）
{% for item in spoiler.predictions %}
- {{ item }}
{% endfor %}
{{ "{{< /spoiler >}}" }}

## 用語集（今回追加・更新分）
{% if glossary_updates %}
{% for term in glossary_updates %}
- **{{ term.term }}**{% if term.reading %}（{{ term.reading }}）{% endif %}: {{ term.description }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
- 今回は既存用語の補足のみでした。
{% endif %}

## 参考リンク（公式中心）
{% for link in reference_links %}
- [{{ link.label }}]({{ link.url }})
{% endfor %}

{% if reference_links %}
{% set official = official_link if official_link else reference_links[0] %}
<p><a class="post-card__more" href="{{ official.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">公式サイトで詳しく読む</a></p>
{% endif %}

{% if affiliate_widgets.amazon %}
<p><a class="post-card__more post-card__more--amazon" href="{{ affiliate_widgets.amazon }}" target="_blank" rel="sponsored noopener">Amazonでチェックする</a></p>
{% endif %}

{% if affiliate_widgets.amazon %}
{{ "{{< affbox title=\"最新巻をAmazonで探す\" desc=\"紙／Kindle版をまとめてチェック\" url=\"" }}{{ affiliate_widgets.amazon }}{{ "\" >}}" }}
{% endif %}

{% if affiliate_widgets.rakuten %}
{{ "{{< affbox title=\"最新巻をRakutenで探す\" desc=\"楽天ポイント還元あり\" url=\"" }}{{ affiliate_widgets.rakuten }}{{ "\" >}}" }}
{% endif %}
